Text: Invesco PureBeta FTSE Developed ex-North America ETF to Issue  -  Dividend of $0.17 (BATS:PBDM) . Stockholders of record on Tuesday, September 24th will be paid a dividend of 0.1747 per share on Monday, September 30th. This represents a dividend yield of 3%.
